  <summary date="2018-03-30T21:25:12Z" status="Introduced in House">Helicopter Fuel System Safety Act

This bill prohibits a person from operating a newly manufactured helicopter in U.S. airspace unless the Federal Aviation Administration certifies that the helicopter's design complies with certain crash resistant fuel system requirements.</summary>
